1.title: Oldelaf

episode of.title: J'irai loler sur vos tombes (TV Series 2009–2011)

1.plot: For the first episode, Poulpe and Davy receive the singer Oldelaf and talk about the movie The Lovely Bones (2009), the comic "X-Men: Magneto Testament", the video game Army of Two: The 40th Day (2010) and the "Battlestar Galactica" board game.

imdb.title: J'irai loler sur vos tombes
plot: In the cave of Ankama Studios, Davy and M. Poulpe receive the personalities of the French geek actuality and talk about video games, movies, series, music and books. They also make comic videos and parodies with their guests.::FUT
